dden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zxd1665702773590.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zxd1665702773590.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zxd1665702773590.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zxd1665702773590\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      state\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property that determines the position and size state of the Form window. Setting state takes precedence over setting position and size properties. Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$windowproperties</span> to set state.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__section_w2225ab1b5b1_w2226ab1b5_w2227ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">NORMAL</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__2\">Restore the form window to the position and\n                        size it had before it was maximized or minimized (Default). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MAXIMIZED</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__2\">Maximize the form. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMIZED</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__2\">Minimize the form. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">CENTERED</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zxd1665702773590__table_d13052e1_d13053e1_d13054e1__entry__2\">Center the form relative to its parent's\n                        window. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__section_zwq_d1w_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d135809e126\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__p_d111623e1_d111624e1_d111625e1\">If you set any of the position and size property\n            values, the window state is forced to <code class=\"ph codeph\">NORMAL</code>, even if the state was\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">MAXIMIZED</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">MINIMIZED</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__p_d111626e1_d111627e1_d111628e1\">In case of conflicting values, setting state takes\n            precedence over setting position and size properties.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__section_xwt_21w_dxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d135809e147\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__ul_f3q_f1w_dxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zxd1665702773590__li_d40451e1_d40452e1_d40453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bch1665702773514.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$windowproperties</a><p>Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617510\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617510\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "state Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 state Window property that determines the position and size state of the Form window. Setting state takes precedence over setting position and size properties. Use $windowproperties to set state. Value Description NORMAL Restore the form window to the position and size it had before it was maximized or minimized (Default). MAXIMIZED Maximize the form. MINIMIZED Minimize the form. CENTERED Center the form relative to its parent's window. Description If you set any of the position and size property values, the window state is forced to NORMAL , even if the state was MAXIMIZED or MINIMIZED . In case of conflicting values, setting state takes precedence over setting position and size properties. Applies To Form Related Links $windowproperties Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}